ink?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FColorluxeExpress%2F&d=g5PjpyBZ77vyHVlMHyzzvTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=05f17044\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ColorluxeExpress/</a><br />\n地址: 灣仔謝斐道316B地下 316B,G/F<br />\n<br />\nDotwell <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DotWellPhoto/ www.dotwellphoto.com.hk \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDotWellPhoto%2F%20www.dotwellphoto.com.hk%20&d=g5PjpyBZ77vyHVlMHyzzvTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=bab919e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DotWellPhoto/ www.dotwellphoto.com.hk </a><br />\n地址: G/F 44 Carnarvon Road Tsim Sha Tsui<br />\n<br />\n明珠數碼攝影沖曬<br />\n地址: 屯門 新墟 Kai Fat Path, 新界屯門啟發徑萬成大廈1號B2地下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">新手/有用文章(外文連結)</span><br />\n<br />\n底片格式<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/底片格式\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%BA%95%E7%89%87%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F&d=g5PjpyBZ77vyHVlMHyzzvTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=fb313893\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/底片格式</a><br />\n<br />\n底片專有名詞資料庫 &ndash; 底片(負片、正片、反轉片)<br />\n<a href=\"http://photoplanet.cc/edit/film/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoplanet.cc%2Fedit%2Ffilm%2F&d=g5PjpyBZ77vyHVlMHyzzvTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=591cfbb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://photoplanet.cc/edit/film/</a><br />\n<br />\n彩色正片與彩色負片的種類與特性<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tps.org.tw/TPS/report/2002/01.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tps.org.tw%2FTPS%2Freport%2F2002%2F01.htm&d=g5PjpyBZ77vyHVlMHyzzvTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=1d4ce926\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tps.org.tw/TPS/report/2002/01.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n菲林感光原理 (內含殘體)<br />\n<a href=\"http://wap.sciencenet.cn/blog-598181-594390.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwap.sciencenet.cn%2Fblog-598181-594390.html&d=g5PjpyBZ77vyHVlMHyzzvTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e1bac990\" target=\"_blank\">http://wap.sciencenet.cn/blog-598181-594390.html</a><br />\n<br />\n彩色軟片的構造 (內含菲林掃描器文章)<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.xuite.net/onlyzeiss/twblog/113459518-彩色軟片的構造--傳統銀鹽底片的核心價值-------無限階調\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.xuite.net%2Fonlyzeiss%2Ftwblog%2F113459518-%E5%BD%A9%E8%89%B2%E8%BB%9F%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E6%A7%8B%E9%80%A0--%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E9%8A%80%E9%B9%BD%E5%BA%95%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC-------%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90%E9%9A%8E%E8%AA%BF&d=g5PjpyBZ77vyHVlMHyzzvTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=acc7544a\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.xuite.net/onlyzeiss/twblog/113459518-彩色軟片的構造--傳統銀鹽底片的核心價值-------無限階調</a><br />\n<br />\n(菲林)天文攝影入門---第六章 感光材料的認識<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkastroforum.net/viewtopic.php?t=871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkastroforum.net%2Fviewtopic.php%3Ft%3D871&d=g5PjpyBZ77vyHVlMHyzzvTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=26c04410\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkastroforum.net/viewtopic.php?t=871</a><br />\n<br />\nBeginners Guide to Processing Film (黑白)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ilfordphoto.com/beginners-guide-processing-film/?___store=ilford_brochure\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ilfordphoto.com%2Fbeginners-guide-processing-film%2F%3F___store%3Dilford_brochure&d=g5PjpyBZ77vyHVlMHyzzvTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=7df40571\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ilfordphoto.com/beginners-guide-processing-film/?___store=ilford_brochure</a>"},{"pid":"6e4d35c9b547837886d0405e797f3a9c8395e8c2","tid":766962,"uid":38997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/134058_29d8d1412f476ce9f841188f61e66eb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F134058_29d8d1412f476ce9f841188f61e66eb9.jpg&h=ed3898ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets